# Xenoblade Chronicles 2 [0100E95004038000] v2.1.0 - 1080p scene resolution
# Derived from emoose's 1440p patch (MOVZ W21,#width / MOVZ W22,#height).
# 1920x1080 makes the scene match the output framebuffer 1:1, removing the
# game's fractional 720->1080 bilinear composite that blurs every frame.

@flag print_values
@flag offset_shift 0x100

@enabled
